{"tid":303522,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"SKOUT 啲人係咪痴線","createTime":"2017-06-30T08:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T11:13:07.000Z","uid":101458,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8751b5b2a36d91e52fba3b0bc1bf0559608ad83c","tid":303522,"uid":101458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"傾唔夠兩句就話要約出嚟<br />\n有啲仲要send J圖黎仲要有埋樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前咁多釣厹/狗女post都唔識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62bd73566528467595f5de3846fd8d8abadbc9a","tid":303522,"uid":57962,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fcbd0d32a259f611ea6ff58f9b69c00b80e01dc","tid":303522,"uid":38923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"仲有人玩skout架咩?<br />\n全部唔係呃錢, 雞, 賓賓"},{"pid":"31a1dc4e35f99b8ed994a13ef7bf6fe9822bc33a","tid":303522,"uid":101458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最on9係有人想喺Skout tinder搵真愛<br />\n之後俾人屌完即棄就怪點解依個世界咁多壞男人<br />\n好心就走去check吓自己係咪屙屎屙撚埋個腦出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後人地講咩又信 話自己搵幾多幾多點叻點叻又信 真係好撚多傻閪架<br />\n仲會有班傻閪以為d男仔真係會為左自己del skout唔玩 以為自己係對方喺skout識嘅最後一個女仔 屌 隔幾日咪又on番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 未有吊厹依樣野之前呃過唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家冇玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女嘅覺得歡場都有真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男嘅就精蟲上腦覺得啲女見到佢地條J會即刻濕晒好想比佢地屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515b6458ca45fc6cd325fabc0cb7396624f2a661","tid":303522,"uid":101458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有人玩skout架咩?<br />\n全部唔係呃錢, 雞, 賓賓</blockquote><br />\n雖然變左賓賓樂園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但都仲有好多人玩"},{"pid":"6470ef3a27271bfb4986dfbf9435308cf9d9d133","tid":303522,"uid":101458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5fea0a191ca4b557ead3612c8d59cbbc3e8f31","tid":303522,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"倫敦金"},{"pid":"8c570d79f37ee02030153589f21ce751f4b90033","tid":303522,"uid":101458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倫敦金</blockquote><br />\n問佢做緊咩佢話睇緊市，超有事業心"},{"pid":"d8df2e11d25baa1d76e7d18a494efcbcb0ef575d","tid":303522,"uid":101458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f58735ecd20d6dc836a2fccee5b48bc635c4f2c","tid":303522,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}